data.description:
Welcome to Fleming Island! Great opportunity to own this lovely 4 bedroom 2 bath nestled in the heart of a desired community.  Features include tile -flooring, newer kitchen stainless steel appliances, elegant pendant lighting, large walk-in closet, spacious bedrooms, roomy two-car garage, and washer & dryer included! Sought after schools and an abundance of shopping and dining near by.
Enjoy family time in your screened in porch that overlooks a large fenced in yard garnished with beautiful flowers, plants, & bushes.
*Roof replaced 2011
**Open House 9/30/2023
